{
  "stem": "22803.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so I, you know, I didn't see them very often.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was the First World War.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was-- was in the army and was wounded several times with all-- you know, in one-- in all these battles that you nowadays hear about in history lessons.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then he-- after the war, he moved to Munich and went into partnership with his-- with his cousin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before he was married, he traveled extensively all over, you know, the Middle East and Italy and Greece.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I have pictures showing some of his travels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After-- after what's-- after the war, of course, there were very bad times already in Germany with the inflation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and there were housing shortages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father owned or bought this house where we lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was an apartment house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But nevertheless, they couldn't live in it 'til it became-- an apartment became vacant, because all this was-- you know, with shortages.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was all regulated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And later on we lived-- when I was born, we lived in this apartment on the first floor in that apartment house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] my-- a short time, my grandparents-- or my grandfather after my grandmother had died, my grandfather lived in two rooms in the back of our apartment.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the-- my last grandparent died when I was four years old, so I have really no memory of-- of any grandparents.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When Hitler came to power was-- by that time I was-- well, he came to power in 1933, so I was 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But after that, of course, business and everything became rather difficult.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, let me think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- the apartment was in a outer suburb of Munich.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just a few more houses.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
